Description: Program that scales images to fit in a bounding box.
 The program, named webnail, can create a web page to display these
 images. A selection of layout styles is available. The default creates
 a vertical list of images that can be scrolled or selected to display
 an image at a larger size. A slideshow mode allows the images to be
